::Zardus/DevilDuer/Mosquitor::

Zardus looks at Wolfgang when Nemesis' transmission reaches him. "Hmm," He 
replies, "Very well, the traitor can wait put him in stasis and put him 
somewhere."

He turns back to Wolfgang. "You were saying?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer nods at Zardus's transmission. He pulls out his gun and points it 
at the feebly struggling FZ. He looks at Nemesis. "Should I shoot or do you 
want to take the honors?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor falls backwards from Dinobot's six shots, each one hitting it's 
mark. Something in his chest explodes in a small explosion. He lands on his 
back on the ground.

"Die maximal!!" His head says over and over again in varying tones before he 
goes into stasis lock.
